title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 16 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 16 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Former Army Ranger, Afghanistan veteran Captain Sean Parnell, joins the show to give firsthand knowledge of unfolding disaster in Afghanistan. Parnell: Blame the suits, not the boots. CNN reporter: "Chanting ‘Death To America!’ but they seem friendly." The Taliban has an official Twitter account, meanwhile former President of the United States remains banned. More Afghanistan veterans call in.
